nodes.text: Tech Mo'r was a male Bith musician who played an Ommni box as a regular member of the band Figrin D'an and the Modal Nodes. Shortly before the Battle of Yavin, Mo'r and the other members of the band played at Chalmun's Spaceport Cantina on the planet Tatooine when Luke Skywalker and Obi-Wan Kenobi visited trying to find a pilot to take them to the planet Alderaan.
